Homepage: https://github.com/lah7/ambiant-mate-colours

Package: ambiant-mate-colours-all
Architecture: all
Depends: ambiant-mate-colours-aqua,
         ambiant-mate-colours-blue,
         ambiant-mate-colours-brown,
         ambiant-mate-colours-orange,
         ambiant-mate-colours-pink,
         ambiant-mate-colours-purple,
         ambiant-mate-colours-red,
         ambiant-mate-colours-teal,
         ambiant-mate-colours-yellow
Replaces: ubuntu-mate-colours-aqua,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-blue,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-brown,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-orange,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-pink,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-purple,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-red,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-teal,
          ubuntu-mate-colours-yellow
Description: Complete collection of Ubuntu MATE variants
 Contains all the coloured GTK themes and icons for:
 - Ambiant-MATE
 - Ambiant-MATE-Dark
 - Radiant-MATE

Package: ambiant-mate-colours-aqua
Architecture: all
Depends: gtk-update-icon-cache,
         ambiant-mate-gtk-themes,
         ambiant-mate-icon-themes
Replaces: ubuntu-mate-colours-aqua
Description: Aqua variant of Ubuntu MATE themes
 Contains aqua coloured versions of Ambiant-MATE, Ambiant-MATE-Dark and
 Radiant-MATE.

